name: Seesaw
description: Swap, Leverage, Farm - a Fully Decentralized and Multi-Chain DeFi Platform. Seesaw Finance is a multi-chain, decentralized, non-custodial ecosystem of DeFi products, protocols, and use cases. Seesaw Token deployed to Binance Smart Chain and will hw deployed on Polygon and Ethereum. Seesaw Finance provides a full list of the services needed for users, who would like to manage crypto assets on the most popular blockchains and p2p exchanging services in a decentralized and open way.
